title: Create the screen with the buttons.
message:
Create the screen with the buttons.

15 buttons.
Top left button always goes to free mode speaking.
Bottom right button is always red.
All buttons except for the free mode speaking button (14 buttons) are configurable using long press.

Still need to hook up the text to actually speak, currently it just displays what it would do.

title: Make toolbar work.
message:
Make toolbar work.

Turns out, the documentation I was following was broken and incorrectly said the toolbar was not supported natively (and required the Toolbar class instead).
But the v7 compatibility library already contains the right logic to make this work.

Since there are no actions associated with the toolbar, it's only item is disabled for now.
